{"tid":104714,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人入黎聽下","createTime":"2017-02-02T09:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T05:19:23.000Z","uid":75474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab4451c7ce31ab1f62d3809705e163720deeb225","tid":104714,"uid":75474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:56:12.000Z","msg":"兩年前 你話想睇我的少女時代<br />\n我即刻仆出黎睇 因為我鐘意你<br />\n睇完同你去左海滂行 諗住表白<br />\n點知你同我講你有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日 大家都各有各生活<br />\n你有仔我亦有女<br />\n我好愛我女朋友 平時一定唔會諗其他女<br />\n<br />\n無意中聽到首小幸運 所有回憶都番哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔會離開我女朋友<br />\n但係我真係覺得好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肥妹呀...究竟你有冇鐘意過我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩年前你身邊有條傻仔好鐘意你<br />\n以前既我 真係好鐘意以前既你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491ae8a8eea2f13479941ee3f970d6f8b3f028d9","tid":104714,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:06:05.000Z","msg":"叫撚完春就番去你女朋友身邊啦柒頭"},{"pid":"9566b5148c143f4f3d125f3f89095f9edf493c22","tid":104714,"uid":71662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:19:23.000Z","msg":"Sad but true"}]}